snippet.title: Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard: NEW EVIDENCE?!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp is suing ex-wife Amber Heard for $50 million, and claims it was HIM who was physically abused by Heard. Now photos of Depp's physical abuse surface... and it's UGLY! Friend Alice Cooper goes to bat for Depp in a new interview.

https://boundingintocomics.com/2019/03/12/new-uncovered-photo-shows-johnny-depp-with-black-eye-as-alice-cooper-defends-the-actor-from-abuse-allegations-made-by-amber-heard/

https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/celebrities/johnny-depp-sues-ex-wife-for-50-million-in-defamation-suit/2019/03/02/4dc41ce4-3d2e-11e9-b10b-f05a22e75865_story.html?noredirect=on&utm_term=.346d2a6050ed

https://twitter.com/cinemapatti/status/1105438073423159296?fbclid=IwAR2tY7YZo8w12cx2xCUHQcFBhkgAOph_Du2_8I4Ykn-eO__rMFW2YBTk1YY
